# PEST Analysis (PESTEL Analysis)
  PESTLE analysis is a strategic planning tool that is used to analyze and monitor various factors that affect the market environment for a business or organization. 
  This tool is especially useful when starting a new business or entering a foreign market. 
  By seeing in the big picture, you can develop a profound understanding of the external environment where the organization operates.


